/>\n然後呢班肉酸左膠就係到話人得一半兌現到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎返奧巴鹿果d垃圾出黎逐個睇丫笨柒"},{"pid":"f5db3a4f14835eb7a7006c15e19ac7c643b8757e","tid":2379704,"uid":144626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"呢D網睇壞腦，當佢抖陰咁抵制最好"},{"pid":"d68044e2261f333365b937086b9d6a29631c61ed","tid":2379704,"uid":248540,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"起左樓主底 發現樓主係一條濕鳩左癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1053adb40817665b1b6108b0c6e5f7d8f74907b7","tid":2379704,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:50:39.000Z","msg":"所以更加要做多屆等佢夠時間兌現"},{"pid":"32485bfe0afe43a462dbbbd4e2e2c77695056b0f","tid":2379704,"uid":58841,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d68044e2261f333365b937086b9d6a29631c61ed","tid":2379704,"uid":248540,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"起左樓主底 發現樓主係一條濕鳩左癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"2樓都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出哂名左膠賤種黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4760ea59865a67af4121e3b919f18ed44be0815c","tid":2379704,"uid":66234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf3f5126f63dc090336c0ce01cd20d09d1c0b8ad","tid":2379704,"uid":3860,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"邊度可以fact check 呢個網係咪fake news"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"你根據返佢既內容<br />\n你搵到反例既 佢咪fake new囉"},{"pid":"43a76c175d9749e1c2c3689bcab8686c514fd2a8","tid":2379704,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"拜登競選承諾應該100%完成，都係推翻Trump舊政同平權"},{"pid":"ac5e71034ea33ec7e1d9bfc8789ed5fe7d434d97","tid":2379704,"uid":1643